.TH "HPC\-COMPOSE\-CANCEL" "1" "" "hpc\-compose 0.1.16" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
hpc\-compose\-cancel \- Cancel a tracked Slurm job
.SH SYNOPSIS
.nf
hpc\-compose cancel [OPTIONS]
.fi
.SH DESCRIPTION
.PP
Cancel a tracked Slurm job by explicit job id or by the latest submission recorded for the compose file.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB-f\fR, \fB--file\fR \fIFILE\fR
Compose specification file to read. Default: compose.yaml.
.TP
\fB--job\-id\fR \fIJOB_ID\fR
Tracked Slurm job id to cancel instead of the latest recorded submission.
.TP
\fB--scancel\-bin\fR \fIPATH\fR
Path to the scancel executable. Default: scancel.
.TP
\fB-h\fR, \fB--help\fR
Print help (see a summary with '\-h').
.SH EXAMPLES
.nf
hpc\-compose cancel \-f compose.yaml
hpc\-compose cancel \-f compose.yaml \-\-job\-id 12345
.fi
